<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910213-0072</DOCNO><DOCID>910213-0072.</DOCID><HL>   Dividend News:   Pitney Bowes Inc.</HL><DATE>02/13/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   PBI</CO><IN>OFFICE EQUIPMENT (OFF)DIVIDENDS (DIV)</IN><LP>   PITNEY BOWES INC. (Stamford, Conn.) -- Directors of thisprovider of mailroom products and services voted to increasethe dividend 13%, to 34 cents a common share from 30 cents.The dividend is payable March 12 to shares of record Feb. 25.Pitney Bowes, which has increased its dividend annually forthe past nine years, said the move reflects the company'scontinued growth.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>